{
  "stem": "6258.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Edmund is E-D-M-U-N-D.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Emanuel is E-M-A-N-U-E-L, Nelken.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] [POINTS] My-- my-- I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We have a neighbor on the second floor, higher floor--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--who is playing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, and as a matter of fact, my mother was Regina Barber, B-A-R-B-E-R.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember very well, but I think that he was born on 12 of April, 19-- 1890 or so.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He lived until May 14 or 15, 1944, when he was sent to gas chamber [INAUDIBLE] and transport of Hungarian to which the transport of men from Plaszow was with it-- together.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I found his file in central files in Auschwitz, and, therefore, I know when he was sent to gas.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was 14 or 15 May 1944.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother was born in Krakow on, I think, 7th of September, 1990-- 9-- 9-- 9-- I'm sorry, 18-- [LAUGHS] 1890, or 18-- 9-- something like this, '95.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, I don't remember exactly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She die here in this country on 19th of March, 1963.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sudden heart attack.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, she was historian, first of all.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But she was doing different things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In particular during the war, everybody had thousands of professions.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But my mother knew how to do accounting and this, and she was doing this for that orphanage in the ghetto for the Jewish children.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My parents had so many interests.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "First of all, music.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody was playing in the family or singing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then father was very much interested in the symphony orchestra in Krakow.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And as a matter of fact, a performer, Alexander Weissenberg, who is a great pianist even here, when he was a small child, my father organized a concert for him in Krakow.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Also the sport, of course.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then theater, opera.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Well, one could hardly say they were hobbies.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
